name: "Resonance Spike"
description:
The Schumann Resonance is the heart beat of the Earth, in the form of an observable frequency. At rest it reads 7.83 Hz. As you can see from this art piece, at stressful or exciting moments it can reach as high as 170 Hz. How can we, as a united consciousness, assist the planet in experiencing more peace? How can we learn to be more symbiotic? How can we express more gratitude?
Spread mindfulness, and carry your emotions as if they are offerings to the Earth.
Pachamama is everywhere, and is everything. Aho, Beautiful Soul!
